BASICS…..

man man
q

man ls


EXPLORING MAN……

sections 1-9

man -f ls (check sections available for ls)

man intro
man 1 intro
man 8 intro


ANOTHER HELPING ARGUMENT…..

whatis ls (same as ‘man -f ls’)

man -k ls (search for various commands, returns all as output)

man -w ls (location of file from where page is rendered)
